replies.body:
Some vague equation that includes:

Kills, Deaths, Assists, Wards, cs, objective (this includes dragons/barons/towers) kills, objective assists, xp, damage dealt, healing recieved, death times, and many other things (including a comparison of all these things to players of the same champ in the same role)

k/d/a isn't the most relevant factor and certainly isn't the majority of the factors that results in a high score, I wish players would understand that ;n;
